This folder contains rule files to be inserted into the PTXdist tree for the program to compile.
Some of these file have been copied and adapted from the PTXdist distribution,
which is distributed under the terms and conditions of the GNU General Public License Version 2.

In particular, no authorship is claimed for the following files:
- paho-mqtt-c.in (from PTXdist 2020.07.0, modified to select the required GLIBC_ANL flag)
- paho-mqtt-c.make (from PTXdist 2020.07.0, modified to build the latest available version)
- protobuf.c (from PTXdist 2020.07.0, modified to build the latest available version)

